original_title: World Series of Fighting 19: Gaethje vs. Palomino
overview: World Series of Fighting 19: Gaethje vs. Palomino was a mixed martial arts event held March 28, 2015 in Phoenix, Arizona, United States. This event aired on NBCSN in the U.S and on Fight Network in Canada.
title: World Series of Fighting 19: Gaethje vs. Palomino
